T*
(BOARD MEETING MATERIALS - Q4 RECAP & Q1 PROJECTION) Tj
T*
(Date: January 15, 2024) Tj
T*
(Confidential - For Board Use Only) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(EXECUTIVE SUMMARY: Q4 PERFORMANCE) Tj
T*
(We closed Q4 with strong momentum, finishing the fiscal year at $11.4M ARR, representing) Tj
T*
(68% YoY growth. Net Revenue Retention \(NRR\) remained healthy at 112%, and our CAC) Tj
T*
(payback period improved to 14 months. The transition to the enterprise-tier pricing) Tj
T*
(model is 80% complete, providing a stable foundation for the upcoming year.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Q4 FINANCIAL HIGHLIGHTS) Tj
T*
(- Revenue: $8.1M Actual vs. $7.9M Plan \(+2.5%\)) Tj
T*
(- Ending ARR: $11.4M) Tj
T*
(- Gross Margin: 74%) Tj
T*
(- Cash on Hand: $18.2M) Tj
T*
(- Burn Rate: $1.1M monthly average) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(PRODUCT & ENGINEERING UPDATE) Tj
T*
(The release of the v3.2 Core Engine was successful, resulting in a 30% reduction in) Tj
T*
(latency for high-volume users. Our roadmap for Q1 focuses on the "Insight Pro" module,) Tj
T*
(which is expected to drive a 15% expansion in ACV for existing accounts. We remain on) Tj
T*
(track for the SOC2 Type II audit completion in March.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Q1 STRATEGIC OUTLOOK & GOALS) Tj
T*
(As we enter Q1, our primary focus is aggressive expansion into the mid-market segment. ) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Q1 TARGETS:) Tj
T*
(- Revenue Target: $8.8M) Tj
T*
(- ARR Target: $12.8M) Tj
T*
(- New Logos: 24) Tj
T*
(- Pipeline Coverage: 3.5x) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(RISK ASSESSMENT & MITIGATION) Tj
T*
(While we see strong demand, we are monitoring the elongation of sales cycles in the) Tj
T*
(enterprise sector. Our mitigation strategy involves a heavier investment in SDR) Tj
T*
(headcount to bolster top-of-funnel activity and a revised "Proof of Value" \(PoV\)) Tj
T*
(framework to accelerate technical validation stages.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(THE "2024 NORTH STAR") Tj
T*
(Our goal for the full year is to reach $20M ARR. This requires maintaining a consistent) Tj
T*
(Q-over-Q growth rate of 15%+. The board is asked to approve the additional $2.5M) Tj
T*
(marketing spend allocated for the Q2 global expansion launch.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(BOARD ACTION ITEMS) Tj
T*
(1. Approval of Q4 Minutes.) Tj
T*
(2. Approval of the 2024 Employee Option Pool expansion \(5%\).) Tj
ET
